videos.description: Michael Porter gets a pass from brother Jontay and finishes in transition, giving Michael his first points since going down with a back injury.
videos.headline: Porter Jr. converts layup for 1st points since injury

videos.description: Jeremiah Tilmon backs his man down in the post and splits the defense to convert a tough layup.
videos.headline: Tilmon backs down defender on tough lay-in

videos.description: Michael Porter tries finishing with a layup in the paint but Nicolas Claxton has other plans and rejects the attempt.
videos.headline: Claxton denies Porter at the rim

videos.description: Yante Maten finds an opening in the lane and soars for a one-handed jam in the first half.
videos.headline: Maten throws down one-handed slam

videos.description: Michael Porter Jr. finds space off a screen and sinks a 3.
videos.headline: Porter Jr. knocks down open 3-pointer

videos.description: Tyree Crump swings it to Teshaun Hightower behind the arc for a long Georgia 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Hightower displays range on deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Jeremiah Tilmon grabs the offensive rebound and throws down a loud two-handed slam for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Tilmon cleans up with emphatic slam

videos.description: Kassius Robertson lofts a pass up to Michael Porter Jr. at the rim for the alley-oop lay-in.
videos.headline: Robertson connects with Porter Jr. for layup

videos.description: Jordan Geist splits through the Georgia defense and sinks a tough layup to earn a trip to the line for a 3-point chance.
videos.headline: Geist sinks tough layup for and-1 chance

videos.description: Jordan Geist launches a deep pass to Michael Porter Jr. for the alley-oop layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Porter Jr. collects and finishes alley-oop lay-in

videos.description: Michael Porter Jr. finds space behind the arc and drains a contested 3-pointer to cut the Georgia lead to 1 late in the second half.
videos.headline: Porter Jr. knocks down big 3-pointer to cut deficit to 1
